def multiplication_table(n):
    table = []
    for i in range(1, n + 1):
        row = []
        for j in range(1, n + 1):
            row.append(i * j)
        table.append(row)
    return table
The nested loop multiplies every i by every j from 1 up to n, appending each finished row to the table before moving to the next i.
